1
00:00:01,330 --> 00:00:02,960
That woman is from
President Nakama's company.

2
00:00:02,960 --> 00:00:04,500
The new legal advisor.

3
00:00:04,710 --> 00:00:06,380
I hear she's brilliant.

4
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:09,330
Wow.
She and President Nakama make a great couple.

5
00:00:09,670 --> 00:00:11,210
That's true.

6
00:00:11,630 --> 00:00:12,630
Stop it!

7
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,880
Seriously, President Nakama...
Instead of choosing someone like her,

8
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,210
he'd be better off with that lawyer.

9
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:19,420
Anyone would be better than this
pathetic little girl.

10
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:21,170
Stop it!

11
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:23,880
I'm no match for Reika-san!

12
00:00:24,630 --> 00:00:25,710
Reika-san is so perfect.

13
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:26,960
So flawless.

14
00:00:27,250 --> 00:00:29,630
So glamorous and smart...
All of that...

15
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:32,830
I know all too well.

16
00:00:41,130 --> 00:00:42,500
What are you looking at?

17
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:44,960
It's nothing.

18
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,130
Not a day went by that I wasn't captivated by her.

19
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:58,460
What are you doing?

20
00:01:01,210 --> 00:01:03,920
Just looking at her
filled my heart with so much love.

21
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:08,790
Looking back now,

22
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:12,500
that was
the happiest time of my life.

23
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,630
That woman...
she trampled all over everything.

24
00:01:16,830 --> 00:01:18,250
She ruined me.

25
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,040
I will never forgive her.

26
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:22,380
I can't just give in

27
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:23,540
to Reika-san's revenge.

28
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:25,790
I absolutely refuse.
